  "original_title": "\u2019\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd\u2019 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The 'resignation letter' is fake",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The President's Secretariat has said that the document being shared on social media as the President's resignation letter is fake.",
        "Meanwhile, President Gotabaya Rajapakse from Singapore had sent his resignation letter to Speaker Mahinda Yappa Abeywardena through the Singapore Embassy in Sri Lanka.",
        "In this case, the Speaker's office announced that it will investigate the legal validity of the said letter and the Speaker will issue a special report in this regard today.",
        "However, it is noteworthy that the letter sent by the President has not been made public by the Speaker so far. (a)"
      ],
